.TH "LIGHTNING-INVOICE-LIST-PENDING" 1 "May 2026" "lightning 0.6.0" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
lightning-invoice-list-pending \- list unpaid invoices
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B lightning invoice-list-pending
.RB [ --limit
.IR N ]
.SH DESCRIPTION
Returns unpaid invoices from
.BR listinvoices .
Default limit is 50.
.PP
Output:
.nf
[{label, payment_hash, amount_msat, expires_at}]
.fi
.SH EXIT STATUS
.TP
.B 0
Always.
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR lightning-invoice-list-paid (1),
.BR lightning-invoice-list-expired (1)
